<h3 id="tools">Tools</h3>
<p>Brown, Blue and White acrylic paint was used to create the grey tones in the painting. Different sized kaerell brushes, a spatula and paper canvas was used for the painting materials.</p>

<h3 id="inspiration">Inspiration</h3>
<p>The theme of the class was Memento Mori, and so we were provided with a variety of skulls and other props to create a painting that encapsulated the idea.</p>
